<component type="desktop">
  <id>majsterklepka-bacade.desktop</id>
  <name>Bank Cash Deposit</name>
  <summary>A simple office application</summary>
  <developer_name>Paweł Sobótka</developer_name>
  <description>
  <p>
     Bank Cash Deposit is software designed for the home office. 
     It can be used in a situation where there is a need to prepare
     a cash payment for print customers, a transfer order. This is
     a GUI application, written using the GTK + library. 
     Works only under Linux OS. Prints an empty form when
     the IBAN account number is incorrect.
 </p>
  <p>What software can do: </p>
  <ul>
	<li>Fill out the form without having to purchase a dedicated print form</li>
	<li>Print the prepared form on a4 and a5 size paper</li>
	<li>Export to pdf format via Print Dialog</li>
  </ul>
 <p>
   Apparently, you need such software. Your customers still use your
   cash and the completed and printed form will impress them.
 </p>
</description>
